<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18Apr1929"><font color="red">18 April 1929</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Thanks for Blast II but what I want is the English-Welsh part! &hellip; The queer allusion to me is in the illustration of that hotel catalogue of marvels. Have you seen the new number of W.L.&apos;s <i>Enemy</i>? A lot of it was read to me but I should prefer the book advertised in <i>Pearson&apos;s W.</i> &lsquo;Want to join the police?&rsquo; </div>
